    <string name="about_tagline">A sideload-only Android IPTV player.</string>
    <string name="about_features">• HLS / DASH / SmoothStreaming / RTSP / progressive playback via ExoPlayer\n• Multi-playlist M3U + XMLTV EPG with periodic refresh (WorkManager)\n• Channel categories, search (name + EPG titles), favorites, channel numbers\n• Combined \"All playlists\" view, per-playlist tabs\n• Full-screen player with channel zap, aspect cycle, audio + subtitle tracks, retro green volume OSD\n• Optional Trinitron CRT skin (portrait remote with number keypad / landscape bezel controls)\n• Share + scan QR for playlists and individual channels (tvtron:// deep link)\n• Manual add / edit / delete of individual channels\n• OTA updates via GitHub Releases</string>
    <string name="about_built_with">Built with ExoPlayer, Room, OkHttp, WorkManager, and Material Design.</string>
